ODEGREE_CHAR

public java.lang.String ODEGREE_CHAR
The character to be used as the degree character. Only textmode applications (and probably awt applications in Java 1.1 and below?) will require to differentiate between different characters, awt / swing components of Java 1.2 and above will use the unicode encoding always!
